No. 10-627. City of New York, New York, Petitioner v. Permanent Mission of India to the United Nations, et al. 562 U.S. 1214, 131 S. Ct. 1553,

179 L. Ed. 2d 297,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 1454. February 22, 2011.

The Acting Solicitor General is invited to file briefs in this case expressing the views of the United States.

Justice Kagan took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
